CGI-Session-ID-sha version 1.01
===============================

This is the README for the inital release of CGI::Session::ID::sha. This allows 
you to use Digest::SHA to generate unique session IDs in CGI::Session.

It includes three modules:

   CGI::Session::ID::sha
   CGI::Session::ID::sha256
   CGI::Session::ID::sha512   

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  CGI::Session
  Digest::SHA

